# Runtime scratch the nightly run (fetch.sh) writes into the app dir. The real
# report data lives in the storage tree, not here; these are regenerated every
# run. Keep them untracked so a run never dirties the repo or turns a routine
# update into a phantom "local changes" conflict.
inputs/
last-run.json
